metadata.name: HEHE SONDER
metadata.description:
#123 Aera Contest Winner

This is my genesis piece of my new art collection where I'll share my humble beginnings as an artist. Ever so slowly, watch me grow over time creating more elaborate works of art. Leveling up as the seasons pass until one day, I can proudly call myself more than a meme artist. The only true masterpiece work that I currently hold to my name and appreciate more than any words can ever say are the frens I made along the way. 

Enjoy this silly creation of two of my favorite things put into one. ~Dorime Ameno~
